data.description: WOW!! Amazing opportunity!! Check out this 2 Bedroom top floor condo that has been totally redone and is ready to move in!! All new Luxury Vinal flooring throughout unit! Large Living room with patio door that leads out to private Balcony. White on white kitchen with new quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, Island/peninsula, and plenty of room for large table!! Good sized bedrooms and closet space in bedrooms! Bathroom has  newly tiled shower and newer vanity! all newer light fixtures and ceiling. Building in great shape and well managed as well.  Newer roof boiler and hot water tank! You will not find a unit like this for the price! Come and see you will love it!!
